snippet.title: DLC 1 & 2 Announce Trailer | Warhammer Age of Sigmar: Realms of Ruin
snippet.description:
Unleash the might of Yndrasta and the destructive power of Gobsprakk on the realm of Ghur in new DLC for Warhammer Age of Sigmar: Realms of Ruin, available from 11th December 2023.

Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/fQKuFVaGSx

Follow us on:

Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/frontierdevelopments
Twitter: https://twitter.com/RealmsOfRuin
